299
00:16:49,720 --> 00:16:50,610
By the way,

300
00:16:50,810 --> 00:16:53,710
she seemed to have taught me
how to become popular.

301
00:16:56,470 --> 00:16:57,870
Does that mean

302
00:16:58,560 --> 00:16:59,960
